{"tid":362001,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)醫神HOUSE 第2季","createTime":"2017-08-16T14:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T21:59:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4db00cd3eced0a91d59cdb258fb80320e631ab","tid":362001,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:42:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=PzCHRg2c2PS3tGfn3tPDNARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c61ad3f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=PzCHRg2c2PS3tGfn3tPDNARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=50259e6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有dailymotion<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=PzCHRg2c2PS3tGfn3tPDNARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3d1e85f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/07/6c/28/076c289a4fc5c97c593d8f066b3ed961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F07%2F6c%2F28%2F076c289a4fc5c97c593d8f066b3ed961.jpg&h=021cb6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n格瑞利&middot;豪斯博士是新澤西州普林斯頓一普蘭斯堡教學醫院的醫生，醫術高明，但為人卻很厭世並且有反社會傾向，他帶領著醫院的一個診斷小組。大部分劇集都是圍繞一個主要病人的病情診斷展開，最開頭時是醫院外的一組鏡頭，顯示病人發病後再切入開場片段。接下來較為典型的劇情就是豪斯的診斷小組試圖對病人作出診斷和治療，並且之前幾次通常會失敗，病人轉入病危階段。他們治療的通常是其他醫院無法確診的疑難病例，豪斯也經常會拒絕接受自己認為沒意思的病例<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=PzCHRg2c2PS3tGfn3tPDNARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=23cb9efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=PzCHRg2c2PS3tGfn3tPDNARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=95f2e447\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7842e889119fbe5de58c6f29346acb54f5d8596f","tid":362001,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3be862aca4199bf2ecdda9b8ba8456bd782396e","tid":362001,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T20:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b8e480df46531139e11227d35c2bda3b9d0fd6","tid":362001,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T21:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87567d32efa9690d406dddad52557cd6b7f4297","tid":362001,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2